{
  "stem": "26585.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Max Schohl, my wife, and my two daughters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How do you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are leaving Germany legally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here are our passports.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he showed him that we had legal-- we are visiting a friend in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother, I guess it just came out, said, we come from hell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the guy said, you better be quiet, because the next apartments are full of SS men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are going-- wherever they were going, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are accompanying actors and actresses for a play, wherever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, ssh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to be quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me tell you a little about myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't trust him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he kept looking at me and kept looking at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he's older than my father, I don't have to worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before we got to the border, he had asked my father for my hand in marriage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I'm sitting here, it's the truth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you'd ever talk to my sister, she would say, can you imagine my sister being so dumb and saying no?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was always the gentleman, said 'I am honored, but my daughter is not even 16.' As a matter of fact, I was 16 that month. 'I would never tell my daughter who to marry and when to marry.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that she is too young.' And he said, 'no, she's not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Greece, we would live in a white house in Saloniki, and you would never have to worry about the Nazis anymore.' And he said, 'Monsieur, I cannot sell my daughter.' And my mother kept going--",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
